textAnnotations.description:
Whille wo wee
prepping Charlie
Fotheringham was
telling me how he'd
arrived at a house to
deliver a packet and
there'd beena note
on the front door:
Do not knoak at the
door-hypnotism in
progreas."
What did you do?
Insked.
irang the bell,
sald Charlie
